Text: Thanks the upload! I'm super excited for all of DC today (for once!), especially this and RH&tO. Super grateful that you guys get us this content so quickly each week :)

you're welcome offcenterfold. lots of good stuff from dc today, although i'm most excited about the death & return of superman omnibus. that and chew 32, saga 11, all new x-men 9, captain america 5 -- great time to be "a kid again"
